MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

94-234. Westlake Village, Inc. v. Cuyahoga Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 92-A-165. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective October 24, 1994.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
